107
00:06:19,513 --> 00:06:24,818
A man his mother sold
for a pitcher of beer
and a black eye.

108
00:06:24,852 --> 00:06:27,988
But don't get me wrong,
I don't hate her.

109
00:06:28,021 --> 00:06:30,691
That's not how
I operate.

110
00:06:30,724 --> 00:06:33,494
You gotta have
a relationship with
someone to hate 'em.

111
00:06:33,527 --> 00:06:37,498
No, man. I was
just a kid trying
to find my way.

112
