done to me before!

199
00:11:49,109 --> 00:11:51,912
- Where is he?
- She took him
with her.

200
00:11:51,945 --> 00:11:53,947
Where do you
think he is?

201
00:11:53,981 --> 00:11:57,217
Sorry. There wasn't
a easier way to tell you.

202
00:11:57,250 --> 00:12:00,821
No, I guess
there wasn't,
now was there?

203
00:12:00,854 --> 00:12:02,522
I'm done.

204
00:12:02,555 --> 00:12:05,225
I just got here.

205
00:12:05,258 --> 00:12:07,027
