and find Rosie

209
00:12:21,274 --> 00:12:23,844
or at least see
my baby boy,

210
00:12:23,877 --> 00:12:26,980
but they kept findin'
reasons to throw me
back in there.

211
00:12:29,016 --> 00:12:31,218
