Rosie again.

212
00:12:31,251 --> 00:12:34,988
- That's it?
- What's it?

213
00:12:35,022 --> 00:12:36,890
What about
your son?

214
00:12:39,059 --> 00:12:41,829
Well, yeah.
I have lots
of children.

215
00:12:41,862 --> 00:12:43,864
