I'm talkin' about.

216
00:12:43,897 --> 00:12:45,966
I'm talkin' about
your natural son,

217
00:12:45,999 --> 00:12:48,301
Charles manson, Jr.

218
00:12:48,335 --> 00:12:50,170
Have you
seen him?

219
