and leno labianca.

227
00:13:13,326 --> 00:13:15,863
Yeah, well, now
what the fuck do you
think about that?

228
00:13:15,896 --> 00:13:18,598
Conspiracy?
What kind of bullshit

229
00:13:18,631 --> 00:13:20,400
