I didn't pull
no trigger.

232
00:13:24,104 --> 00:13:26,306
I didn't stab no one.
They got nothing.

233
00:13:26,339 --> 00:13:28,441
Well, they claim
that Susan atkins

234
00:13:28,475 --> 00:13:31,211
told her cellmate
everything.

235
00:13:35,448 --> 00:13:37,885
You didn't get
out of jail until

236
00:13:37,918 --> 00:13:40,220
long after Rosalie
divorced you.

237
00:13:41,955 --> 00:13:45,192
I tried
to get out.

238
00:13:45,225 --> 00:13:47,928
I got out a while
after that.

239
00:13:47,961 --> 00:13:51,198
Got myself,
another wife,
another kid.

240
00:13:51,231 --> 00:13:54,034
You haven't had contact
with them either?

241
00:13:54,067 --> 00:13:58,038
No, man. Had to go back
in for another ten-stretch.

242
00:13:58,071 --> 00:14:01,208
Tried to cash a check
the government didn't
want me to cash.

243
00:14:01,241 --> 00:14:03,276
