Charlie.

244
00:14:03,310 --> 00:14:06,479
Kennedy,
the civil rights movement,

245
00:14:06,513 --> 00:14:08,381
the beginning
of Vietnam.

246
00:14:08,415 --> 00:14:09,883
Must've been
a real eye-opener

247
00:14:09,917 --> 00:14:11,351
when you got out
after that.

248
00:14:11,384 --> 00:14:14,254
Nah, man.
Nah, it wasn't
